{
  "stem": "942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we are taken to a neighboring city, the capital city of our province, which is called Kassa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were some people who were yelling at us, some derogatory remarks, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, stinking Jews, you know, you're going to get what's coming to you, things like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember being very ashamed that I was marching in this, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people were yelling these terrible things at me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a very-- I felt really terrible, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, this is my town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, where I was born, and I lived here for 14 years, and I could sense that I am different than they are, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are standing on-- on a firm ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are at home, and I don't know where I am going, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt really bad, you know, and very uncertain of what's going to happen to me, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I could-- so these were the feelings that I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were not treated very nicely, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So then, we arrived at the train station, and we were put on the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I said, we came into Kassa, and we were marched down to the-- to this big synagogue yard where they-- the Jewish community was looking after all these people brought in from all over the province.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kassa was the provincial city of the province.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the system in Hungary was that they were collecting all these Jews into central places in the capital cities of the provinces.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The plans were, you know-- which we didn't know-- but these were the plans to bring us to near major railroad yards where they can put us on trains and ship us straightforward to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
